title: Chwast Food
typeOfFood: Vegan, Western, Fast food, Take-out, Polish
description: Opened in 2014 as Best Seler, meaning "celery" in Polish, and changed name in 2015. Offers vegan burgers with focus on Polish flavors. Burger patties are made from celery, millet, beet root, tofu, mushroom, seitan, and veggies. Gluten free options.
